: T11.1 → T11.2 → T11.3 → T11.4\n690:     ↓              ↓\n691: T12.1 → T12.2 → T12.3 → T12.4 → T12.5\n692:     ↓              ↓\n693: T13.1 → T13.2 → T13.3 → T13.4 → T13.5 → T13.6\n694: ```\n695: \n696: ---\n697: \n698: ## Verification Commands\n699: \n700: | Task | Verification Command |\n701: |------|----------------------|\n702: | Metadata model tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py -v` |\n703: | KubernetesProvider tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py -v` |\n704: | AgentCubeProvider tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py -v` |\n705: | PublishRuntime tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_runtime.py -v` |\n706: | DockerService tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py -v` |\n707: | CLI tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_cli.py -v` |\n708: | Integration tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py -v` |\n709: | All tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v` |\n710: | Coverage | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` |\n711: | Publish command help | `kubectl-agentcube publish --help` |\n712: | Lint check | `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n713: | Type check | `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n714: | Import test | `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime import PublishRuntime\"` |\n715: | Provider imports | `python -c \"from agentcube.services import KubernetesProvider, AgentCubeProvider\"` |\n716: \n717: ---\n718: \n719: ## Acceptance Criteria\n720: \n721: - [ ] `AgentMetadata` extended with `k8s_deployment`, `agent_id`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port`\n722: - [ ] `KubernetesProvider` class with `__init__`, `_sanitize_name`, `_ensure_namespace`, `_create_deployment`, `_create_service`, `wait_for_deployment_ready`, `deploy_agent`, `get_agent_status`, `delete_agent`\n723: - [ ] `AgentCubeProvider` class with `__init__`, `_sanitize_name`, `_ensure_namespace`, `deploy_agent_runtime`, `get_agent_runtime`\n724: - [ ] AgentRuntime CR body template with correct spec structure\n725: - [ ] `DockerService` enhanced with `push_image`, `tag_image`, `login`, `get_local_image_url`\n726: - [ ] `PublishRuntime` class with `__init__`, `publish`, `_prepare_image_for_publishing`, `_prepare_local_image`, `_prepare_cloud_image`, `_publish_cr_to_k8s`, `_publish_k8s`, `_update_publish_metadata`\n727: - [ ] Provider validation: invalid provider raises `ValueError`\n728: - [ ] `publish` Typer command with all options: `--workspace`, `--version`, `--image-url`, `--image-username`, `--image-password`, `--description`, `--region`, `--cloud-provider`, `--provider`, `--node-port`, `--replicas`, `--namespace`, `--verbose`\n729: - [ ] Rich Progress spinner during publish\n730: - [ ] Success output: agent name, ID, endpoint, deployment type, namespace\n731: - [ ] Error handling via `_handle_error()`\n732: - [ ] Error recorded in metadata before exception\n733: - [ ] NodePort validation (30000-32767 range)\n734: - [ ] Required field validation: `router_url`, `workload_manager_url` for agentcube provider\n735: - [ ] `image_url` required for local build mode\n736: - [ ] Unit tests for KubernetesProvider (init, sanitize, deploy, wait, status, delete)\n737: - [ ] Unit tests for AgentCubeProvider (init, deploy, patch, get)\n738: - [ ] Unit tests for PublishRuntime (publish, prepare image, metadata update)\n739: - [ ] Unit tests for DockerService publish methods\n740: - [ ] Unit tests for CLI command\n741: - [ ] Integration tests for publish workflow\n742: - [ ] `kubernetes>=28.0.0` dependency added\n743: - [ ] All providers exported from `services/__init__.py`\n744: - [ ] `PublishRuntime` exported from `runtime/__init__.py`\n745: - [ ] All tests pass with >80% coverage\n746: - [ ] Ruff lint passes\n747: - [ ] MyPy type check passes\n748: \n749: ---\n750: \n751: ## File Changes Summary\n752: \n753: | File | Action | Lines Changed | Description |\n754: |------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n755: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Modify | ~20 | Add `k8s_deployment`, `agent_id`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port` fields |\n756: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | Create | ~150 | `KubernetesProvider` class for standard Deployment/Service |\n757: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | Create | ~100 | `AgentCubeProvider` class for AgentRuntime CR |\n758: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Modify | ~40 | Add `tag_image`, `login`, `get_local_image_url`, enhance `push_image` |\n759: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export `KubernetesProvider`, `AgentCubeProvider` |\n760: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Create | ~180 | `PublishRuntime` class with publish orchestration |\n761: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export `PublishRuntime` |\n762: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` | Modify | ~60 | Add `publish` command with Typer options |\n763: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py` | Create | ~200 | Unit tests for KubernetesProvider |\n764: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py` | Create | ~150 | Unit tests for AgentCubeProvider |\n765: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_runtime.py` | Create | ~250 | Unit tests for PublishRuntime |\n766: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py` | Modify | ~80 | Unit tests for DockerService publish methods |\n767: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_cli.py` | Create | ~100 | Unit tests for CLI publish command |\n768: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_integration.py` | Create | ~120 | Integration tests for publish workflow |\n769: | `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` | Modify | ~10 | Add `kubernetes>=28.0.0` dependency |\n770: \n771: ---\n772: \n773: ## Implementation Notes\n774: \n775: - **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n776: - **Reference implementation**: `BuildRuntime` in `build_runtime.py` provides similar pattern\n777: - **Provider pattern**: Two providers with similar structure, validate required fields differently\n778: - **AgentRuntime CR**: Custom Resource from Volcano AgentCube project\n779: - **Name sanitization**: DNS-compliant, lowercase, max 63 chars, replace special chars with `-`\n780: - **NodePort range**: 30000-32767 (Kubernetes standard range)\n781: - **Deployment timeout**: 120 seconds default, poll every 2 seconds\n782: - **Rich Progress**: Use `SpinnerColumn` + `TextColumn` for publish spinner\n783: - **Error recording**: Always record error in metadata before raising exception\n784: - **Option overrides**: CLI options override metadata fields\n785: - **Image preparation**: Different path for local vs cloud build mode\n786: - **CR patch on conflict**: If AgentRuntime CR exists, patch instead of create (handle 409)\n787: \n788: ---\n789: \n790: ## Implementation Timeline\n791: \n792: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n793: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n794: | Phase 1: Metadata Model Extensions | T1.1-T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n795: | Phase 2: KubernetesProvider Class | T2.1-T2.10 | Pending | 0% |\n796: | Phase 3: AgentCubeProvider Class | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n797: | Phase 4: DockerService Enhancements | T4.1-T4.4 | Pending | 0% |\n798: | Phase 5: PublishRuntime Class | T5.1-T5.11 | Pending | 0% |\n799: | Phase 6: CLI Command Implementation | T6.1-T6.2 | Pending | 0% |\n800: | Phase 7: Unit Tests - KubernetesProvider | T7.1-T7.10 | Pending | 0% |\n801: | Phase 8: Unit Tests - AgentCubeProvider | T8.1-T8.8 | Pending | 0% |\n802: | Phase 9: Unit Tests - PublishRuntime | T9.1-T9.13 | Pending | 0% |\n803: | Phase 10: Unit Tests - DockerService | T10.1-T10.5 | Pending | 0% |\n804: | Phase 11: Unit Tests - CLI Command | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n805: | Phase 12: Integration Tests | T12.1-T12.5 | Pending | 0% |\n806: | Phase 13: Dependencies & Validation | T13.1-T13.6 | Pending | 0% |\n807: \n808: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/77 tasks)**\n\n(End of file - total 808 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Valu